SeaWorld Group Events Company Picnics and Outings Private Events Options Meetings / Banquets Group Tickets / Youth Programs Where Energy, Diversity and Purpose Meet Planning a gathering of 15 or more? Save on your next group event and unlock an experience unlike any other. At SeaWorld, extraordinary moments are our promise. Here, unexpected encounters and unbelievable events create unforgettable experiences like nowhere else in Orlando. Imagine pairing world-class roller coasters with a diverse array of immersive experiences, all infused with your personal touch. Create memorable corporate events and unique group outings that are distinctly SeaWorld®. From exhilarating activities for both adults and children to team-building moments that leave lasting impressions, SeaWorld offers it all. Whether your group is bonding on Mako, Orlando’s tallest, fastest, and longest coaster, marveling at penguins in our all-new Antarctica realm, or networking on the serene, sandy shores of Discovery Cove, every moment will be a sensory delight. Your team will return to the office buzzing with excitement, long after the day is done.

Unexpected encounters... unbelievable events. This is SeaWorld's promise, where one-of-a-kind experiences abound.

Combine world class coasters with a diversity of experiences unmatched in Orlando, topped off by a personal flavor all your own. That’s the perfect formula for unexpected encounters and unbelievable corporate events that are uniquely SeaWorld®.

Save when you bring 15 or more guests for your group outing.

Fun group activities for adults and kids alike are what unbelievable events are made of. Whether your event includes team bonding on Orlando’s tallest, fastest and longest coaster Mako, seeing penguins up-close at Antarctica: Empire of the Penguin® or networking on the white, sandy beaches of Discovery Cove, it will be an immersive delight for the senses that will have your team singing its praises all the way back to the office and beyond.

Add to cart Show more Your Visit Makes a Difference See How Close Your Visit Makes a Difference A portion of every ticket purchased goes towards the rescue, rehabilitation and return of thousands of animals that need our help. 41,000+ Rescues Over the past 50 years, SeaWorld has rescued more than 41,000 animals. 24 7 365 Our SeaWorld Rescue Team is available 24/7/365. 300+ Studies We are the worldwide leader in animal research. Our experts have published more than 300 scientific studies. Working Together We are proud partners with renowned organizations like Humane Society of the United States. $10M Pledge SeaWorld has pledged $10,000,000 to fund research and conservation for killer whales in the wild. Events that Matter When you book an event at SeaWorld you are helping support the efforts of the SeaWorld rescue team. Over the last 50 years SeaWorld's rescue teams have helped more than 41,000 animals in need. Company Picnics and Outings SeaWorld Orlando offers company picnic locations and outing options for business meetings, corporate events, convention attendees, and large groups. Learn More Private Event Options SeaWorld Orlando offers a variety of venue options for private events. Learn More Meetings / Banquets Specifically designed to provide a more casual meeting experience, Ports of Call and the Sea Harbor Pavilions are ideal for buffet-style functions and receptions for groups as large as 1,500. Four covered pavilions center around a spacious central courtyard laced with lush greenery and majestic palm trees. Learn More Group Tickets / Youth Programs SeaWorld Orlando offers special group rates and package options for business meetings, corporate events, convention attendees, large groups, along with school, scout or youth groups. From free live concerts to events fit for foodies to festive holiday celebrations, we’ve packed our calendar full of family fun all year long.

Enjoy access to American Sign Language (ASL) - interpreted shows and presentations and a welcoming environment where you can fully experience SeaWorld's incredible attractions.

Select Nights, Sept. 5 - Nov. 1, 2025
A new terror has surfaced, and there’s nowhere to hide. Howl-O-Scream has washed ashore at SeaWorld Orlando, and this time, the fear is everywhere.

SeaWorld Orlando Events FAQs
How can I find information about upcoming events at SeaWorld Orlando?
Check our
event page
for the latest updates on upcoming events, dates, and details. Don’t miss out on the best events going on in Orlando.
What are the best family-friendly events at SeaWorld Orlando?
Most of all SeaWorld
events in Orlando
are family-friendly, featuring kid-friendly activities, character meet-and-greets, and more. For the best experience, an
annual pass
gives you unlimited access to the events and significant savings.
What is considered the best foodie experience event in Orlando?
The Seven Seas Food Festival at SeaWorld Orlando takes the crown as the ultimate foodie experience. Taking place on select dates from February to May, it invites you to indulge in an exceptional culinary journey. Sip and sample your way around the world, relishing exciting flavors, local craft beers, and live performances.
What is the best event in the Orlando area for kids?
Join the festivities at SeaWorld Orlando for
Elmo's Birthday Celebration
during select dates in January and February. It's the perfect opportunity for kids to celebrate Elmo's special day with meet-and-greets, an interactive DJ dance party, and many delightful surprises. SeaWorld Orlando is also celebrating Sesame Street Land’s 5th birthday in 2024 with an all-new parade, Sesame Visiting Friends and more!
What private event options does SeaWorld Orlando offer?
SeaWorld Orlando provides a range of
private event options
, including Company Picnics and Outings, private event venues, and meetings/banquets.
What's the best way to enjoy SeaWorld's Orlando events?
Purchase an Annual Pass! With an
Annual Pass
, you can access all events throughout the year. It's the most cost-effective way to enjoy the full spectrum of SeaWorld Orlando's events, from seasonal celebrations to exclusive experiences, ensuring you never miss a moment of excitement.
Where is the best Mardi Gras event in Orlando?
Let the good times roll at SeaWorld Orlando! Join us in February for a Mardi Gras celebration as part of our Seven Seas Food Festival. Enjoy limited-time food, cocktails, vibrant entertainment, and live music in true Mardi Gras style.
